cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is about multilingual neural machine translation, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses different modeling decisions and trade-offs, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions using a large-scale dataset, which could indicate that it belongs to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) if the dataset includes image data.
